high_descs: Turn around and step forward to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Look down to face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Step to the right to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Step right to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Step left to face the fridge.
Cool the piece of apple in the fridge and remove it.
Turn right and cross the room and turn left to face the microwave.
Place the piece of apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a piece of apple plus place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, go halfway across the room and turn left to the counter.
Pick up the knife behind the apple on the counter.
Look down at the apple.
Cut the apple on the counter.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the knife in the freezer.
Turn right and go back to the apple on the counter.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Go back to the fridge.
Chill the slice of apple in the fridge and pick it back up.
Turn left and go across the room to the microwave.
Put the slice of apple in the microwave to the right of the mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right twice to face the counter with the knife.
Pick up the knife off of the counter.
Face the apple with the knife.
Slice the apple with the knife.
Take the knife over to the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Walk back over to the apple slices on the counter.
Pick up an apple slice off of the counter.
Walk back to the fridge.
Place the apple slice in the fridge then take it back out.
Take the apple slice to the microwave.
Place the apple slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the chilled apple slice in the microwave.
